Canada to Review Encana, PetroChina Agreement, Clement Says

-- B y   D a v i d   S c a n l a n
-- 
2011-02-11T14:05:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-11/canada-will-review-encana-petrochina-agreement-industry-minister-says.html
The Canadian government will review
the investment by PetroChina Co. in a natural gas project with  Encana Corp . The investment is subject to a review under the
Investment Canada Act, Industry Minister Tony Clement said in a
statement today. Canada will approve the sale of the gas assets
if it provides a “net benefit” to the country, Clement said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Scanlan at 
 dscanlan@bloomberg.net  